lead_paragraph: In a battle as fluid and as furious as that of the clashing tanks in Libya it would be foolhardy to predict the outcome. It is only possible to tell what has happened thus far. This Premier Churchill did very clearly in his report to the House of Commons yesterday on the first week of operations.
